        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         I really never understood people that pull with Vex. Why ? First, as a dot, it sucks. Second, while mob runs after you with vex on, dot does not do full damage. I say: pull with splurt. The first ticks of splurt dont do any significant damage anyway. Pathing in the graveyard allows you to hit the mob with darkness before he reaches you. Fear and then land vex. Starting with Vex in a fear-kiting situation is anything but efficient in my book. But that's just me :)</P><P><font size=1>Iranicus Darkseeker<BR>Warlock of Ayonae Ro<BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=12328" target="_blank">My Gear</a></font id=size1><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
