        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Actually, the most efficient method I have found  in the graveyard is to pull with splurt, darkness and fear, and then BoD.  I do NOT use vexing because it is overkill on these guys.  I DO use BoD rather than letting the pet do all the work because the extra damage allows the timing of the kill to be perfect.  Using these spells and a monk pet, all 7 of the guards will get killed and the roamer will repop just as you are killing the seventh one allowing you to start over.  From there on, one guard pops after each kill, allowing for no downtime, and maximum exp as you are killing every guard and there is always one target to pull.  If u have Demi Lich, using this method you will be able to pull for hours nonstop and have very few mana or hp worries.  I breezed through 56 and 57 this way, now i am 58 and just started root dotting gargoyles.</P><P>Ozznusyen Zuulavv<BR>58th Defiler<BR>Brell Serilis</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
