        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Darkvane were you hunting at Graveyard? if so park pet on cathedral wall.  Pull one of the guards just outside of graveyard to the left with splurt.  run to pet and root the guard halfway to you.  Proceed to  darkness, ignite blood and sit. once he breaks root, fear and sic pet on em. BoD ,lich and sit.  Once hes dead pull roamer that comes to graveyard entrance. do same thing.  For two guards at stairs, cast darkness on one and wait till undarknessed one is at graveyard ent and then feign death.  darknessed one will be stuck and other will go back to spawn point, wait till he is there.  Then unfeign and pull darknessed one to pet and proceed to kill. GL (=</P><P></P><P>Edited by - Osso Lychwake on 07/16/2002  12:20:35<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
