        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         You havent screwed yourself.  Kill guards at the bank area if you are KoS to coterie until you get to dubious...then you can go to the graveyard if you want.  Also, I have hunted here since 54.  I did have problems with adds until 56.  Splitting them is easy.  Darkness one and FD immediately.  Other one will go back to spawn and the darknessed one will stand there.  Then get up and lead the darknessed one into the graveyard and fear kite.  It is really simple and no need to root since the pet changes.  Fear kiting is the way to go on the guards.  Pet, splurt and BoD is all the damage you will need and you should be able to kill all 7 guards, starting with the roamer.</P><P>Oznusyen Zuulavv<BR>58th Defiler<BR>Brell Serilis</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
      </tr>

