        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Coterie faction isn't vital. I started off KOS to them and had no trouble the entire time I was KOS, and I was KOS for quite some time. You've got a second or three to run once the undead spawn, use it.</P><P>Or just fear them, they poof or get killed by guards. I'm not sure, but they don't come back.<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
