        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         The undead despawn in about 20 sec if not aggroed.</P><P>You can bank even if you don't kill the guards. There's two guards inside but I've never had them aggro when I start casting FD. The bankers have never aggroed but they've been green since I started banking at 57th level.</P><P><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=200535" target="_blank">Loreana Shahnra</a></P><P>58th Level Human Defiler of Innoruuk<BR>Tribunal</P><P>'And the the Hate still shapes me,<BR>So hold me until it sleeps.'<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
